Life at Level 3
Many companies say they have the ability to change the world. At Level 3 Communications, we mean it. Connectivity is revolutionizing the world, and Level 3 is at the forefront.




Diversity and Inclusion
The very nature of our business – connecting and protecting the networked world – is inherently global, facilitating the exchange of ideas from every corner of the world.




Our Values 
Our values drive how we treat our employees and how our employees treat each other.








 
Welcome from the CEO


My sincerest thanks for considering a career at Level 3 Communications. I’d like to tell you why I think it’s one of the best decisions you could ever make.

As a premier global communications provider and operator of a 200,000-mile fiber network, Level 3 has authored many exciting chapters in the history of communications technology – and we’re poised to write many more. Connectivity has become an indispensable commodity for modern living, and we are in the vanguard of not only interconnecting more and more of our world but also creating solutions that shape how that world lives, learns and works.
Despite its relative infancy, modern communication is already as ingrained in everyday life as running water. It’s a field that can uniquely offer the dynamism of young, disruptive technology, but at the global scale of, say, electricity or cars. What this all means is that at Level 3, you have the uncommon opportunity to sculpt your career, our company and the very evolution of an industry that touches the entire human population.
Level 3 is powered by a global team of more than 13,000 of the brightest minds and biggest imaginations on the planet. We are looking for employees across all areas of expertise to help us build tomorrow’s technology. We commit to providing you with a great work environment, opportunities for career growth and the chance to be part of something extraordinary.
I’ll leave you with our employee value proposition – a promise for which I hold myself personally responsible:
Our winning team is the essence of today and tomorrow’s communications. At Level 3, people combine challenging work with ingenuity to help each other thrive in our global, fast-paced and growing company. We believe that speaking the truth, doing what we say we are going to do and having passion for delivering an exceptional customer experience drives our success. Level 3 makes global communications possible; together with our customers, we are changing the world. Come grow with us and be part of something that’s important and exciting.
We are changing the world for the better. I hope you’ll come change it with us.
— Jeff Storey, Level 3 Chief Executive Officer






 

