Voice Complete






















Level 3® Voice Complete® 
Make the Move to SIP Trunking at Your Own Pace.
Transitioning from legacy services to more efficient business unified communications is a journey, not an event. Whether you’re starting to explore the advantages of SIP or looking to launch full-blown unified communications, the first leg of your trek is enabling enterprise SIP trunking services. 

Level 3 Voice Complete can be your guide. Our global communication solution combines SIP and ISDN-PRI services, inbound and outbound calling, and an array of business features. Easily enable simple conversations, remove administration burden and drive business growth.


Voice Complete Brochure



 


Why Level 3 Sip Trunking ServicesExperience sophisticated enterprise voice and SIP trunking technologies via an out-of-the-box design and eliminate the frustration of a typical patchwork approach. One vendor, one contract and unified SLAs. 
Level 3 Voice Complete offers multi-continent bandwidth sharing from a single pool of calling resources. Take advantage of all-inclusive, concurrent call-path (CCP) pricing that can help lower your total ownership costs. And built-in failover adds protection without having to purchase additional CCPs.  
Manage less premise technology and forget constant voice infrastructure upgrades. PRI and SIP connections are supported as well as PBXs, and we handle all conversions. You can add new locations and adopt new technologies while leveraging your existing investments. 
Unified Communication Support
Level 3 Voice Complete enables all major unified communication products and applications. Choose who, what and when. Our service is certified on multiple platforms, including Avaya®, Cisco® and Microsoft®. We’re ready when you are. 
Level 3 Voice Complete. “Complete” isn’t just in the name. It’s in the solution. 



Read MoreIHS SIP Scorecard: Level 3 Takes Top Spot 

 
 

How and Why It Works 


Level 3 Voice Complete Benefits

Simplify Management and Help Lower Costs: SIP trunking from headquarters or other aggregation sites replace PRI circuits to deliver calls. 
Easily add Incremental Bandwidth: Concurrent call paths (CCPs) can be pooled and shared at any Level 3 Voice Complete equipped site. 
Eliminate the Need to Add Gateways and Reconfigure: PRI and SIP connections are supported as well as PBXs. 
Protect from Disruption:  Level 3 Voice Complete includes built-in failover and redundancy. 

Level 3 Voice Complete Details

SIP trunking and PRI connections to the public switched telephone network (PSTN) do not require premise conversion gear.
Local, long distance/national, toll free/freephone and international destination-calling ability.
Flexible access options via Level 3 MPLS/IP VPN, Level 3 Dedicated Internet Access or bring your own bandwidth.
Global pricing model with flexible invoicing options. 
Customer portal to efficiently manage solution features.
Free intra-enterprise calling.

 












Frost & Sullivan VoIP Access and SIP Trunking Award
 

Learn More











