Overview Level 3 Communications, Llc is an internet access company in Broomfield. This private company was founded in 1997. With 639 other locations, the organization is a member of a large, complex corporate structure.Revenue The organization generates $1.59B in estimated sales.Employees Level 3 Communications, Llc employs 5,300 people of which 2,100 employees are estimated to work at this location. In Broomfield, an average company has between 2 and 56 employees, making Level 3 Communications, Llc about 72 times larger than the average company and therefore one of the largest employers in the area.
 





